column14: youtube is very old, could be from same person or different
website is a Substack; he is posting campaign videos onto his pre-existing personal youtube page
dont think there is a facebook, option on campaign website felt more like to share the website
was campaign website for 2 years ago, might be used again - https://www.electkevinclark.com
facebook link is correct, they havent updated the url for the current race
has a bluesky, but doesnt look like campaign at all, https://bsky.app/profile/airborne1970.bsky.social
this bluesky might be his, but have no idea - https://bsky.app/profile/ralph-scott.bsky.social
website wouldnt load at all for me, be careful when checking it
when double checking, make sure to include the "R", there is a different adam smith running in a different state
this might be his, should be double checked - https://www.tiktok.com/@_sid.sharma_
twitter was used for previous campaign, https://x.com/katebarrcantwin?lang=en
facebook account hasnt been used since 2023
website for campaign is for his governor run in 2024, not senate - https://www.williamshouseusa.com/ , for all other social media, all could found is personal sites, nothing campaign related
website for governor was flagged by my computer, and refused to open it, be careful - https://orrickquick.com/contact/
